cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use TourMart in your research, please cite this software."
type: software
title: "TourMart: A Parametric Audit Instrument for Commission Steering in LLM Travel Agents"
version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-04-21"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/usmliuyao/tourmart"
abstract: >
  TourMart is a measurement instrument for LLM-OTA commission governance.
  Two parameters—lambda (weight of message-induced perceptions) and kappa
  (cap on net message-induced welfare adjustment)—are governance knobs, not
  research hyperparameters. This package reproduces the paper's headline
  numbers from raw data.

authors:
